Rehn Says Portugal Aid Only Possible With Finland, YLE Reports

-- B y   D i a n a   b e n - A a r o n
-- 
2011-04-26T16:03:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-26/rehn-says-portugal-aid-only-possible-with-finland-yle-reports.html
The European Union won’t prepare an
alternative package to aid  Portugal  if  Finland  doesn’t
participate, said Olli Rehn European Commissioner for Economic
and Monetary Affairs, according to Finland’s state-owned
broadcaster YLE.  “The use of the European stability fund requires
unanimity,” YLE cited Rehn as saying on its website.  Click here for web link in Finnish  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
